PM2 is used as daemon for NodeJS server
All pm2 commands must run as root, because server need root privileges in order
to run poweroff and reboot commands.

PM2 commands:
    -> sudo pm2 ls -> list all active scripts
    -> sudo pm2 restart all -> restarts all scripts
    -> sudo pm2 restart [script_name] -> restart specific scripts
    -> sudo pm2 monit -> scripts logs